data.description: CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS - Come see this beautiful 3 Bedroom, 3 full Bathroom + Bonus Room And POOL on Panama City Beach!!! Located in the North Lagoon Heights community you find yourself only a short commute to the Navy Base, St. Andrew's State Park and public boat ramps with plenty of shopping & local dining nearby. This home features single story living at its best, with 2 Master Bedroom suites, covered porch / patio, a large fenced in backyard with your own private pool and a 2-car garage with plenty of driveway space. If you are looking for a place in PCB to call your own then you are going to want to see this home! All dimensions are approximate and should be verified if deemed important.
